<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0" xml:id="zend.filter.set.int"><info><title>Int</title></info>
    

    <para>
        <classname>Zend_Filter_Int</classname> allows you to transform a sclar value which contains
        into an integer.
    </para>

    <section xml:id="zend.filter.set.int.options"><info><title>Supported options for Zend_Filter_Int</title></info>
        

        <para>
            There are no additional options for <classname>Zend_Filter_Int</classname>.
        </para>
    </section>

    <section xml:id="zend.filter.set.int.basic"><info><title>Basic usage</title></info>
        

        <para>
            A basic example of usage is below:
        </para>

        <programlisting language="php"><![CDATA[
$filter = new Zend_Filter_Int();

print $filter->filter('-4 is less than 0');
]]></programlisting>

        <para>
            This will return '-4'.
        </para>
    </section>
</section>
